flowchart TD
    A[New Feature or Architectural Change] --> B{New trust boundary or major data flow change?}
    B -->|Yes| C[Create or Update DFD and Abuse Stories]
    B -->|No| D[Reuse Existing Threat Model and Review Assumptions]

    C --> E[Apply STRIDE]
    D --> E

    E --> F{Processes personal or sensitive data?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Apply LINDDUN as an additional privacy lens]
    F -->|No| H[Define Security Requirements]

    G --> I[Define Security and Privacy Requirements]
    H --> I
    I --> J[Implement Controls and Add Pipeline Gates]
